The room he is in is as broken as he is, but he is not defeated. The open balcony offers a way out, but the man has too determined a look to be contemplating suicide. The body language suggests he is forming a plan of action. His clothes look worn, but adequate. The professional haircut and white shirt would indicate he wasn't working in the trades.
